<plot>Peter, on his first business trip abroad, is sent to a rundown farming town which was crippled when a deadly pig flu wiped out it's stock. By chance Peter finds accommodation at the La Serena Bed and Breakfast where he is welcomed in by the enigmatic landlady, Maria. When he checks in he unsuspectingly becomes entangled in a treacherous mystery that is the dark underbelly of the sleepy town.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?305394</url></doc>
